---
title: get_validators_custody_requirement (fulu-validator)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_sum : total_node_balance = sum(state.validators[index].effective_balance for index in validator_indices)
    q_sum --> q_divide : count = total_node_balance // BALANCE_PER_ADDITIONAL_CUSTODY_GROUP
    q_divide --> q_clamp : result = min(max(count, VALIDATOR_CUSTODY_REQUIREMENT), NUMBER_OF_CUSTODY_GROUPS)
    q_clamp --> [*] : return result

    note right of q_clamp
        INV: Return value is always >= VALIDATOR_CUSTODY_REQUIREMENT (8)
        INV: Return value is always <= NUMBER_OF_CUSTODY_GROUPS
        INV: total_node_balance is non-negative (sum of effective balances)
    end note
